Nrvnqsr Chaos
==The chaos==

A user with as many [[sockpuppets]] as God himself, Nrvnqsr Chaos(Pronounced KNEE-ROW KAY-OWS)is an all-purpose [[Troll|warrior]], [[lawyer|E-Lawyer]], racer, and pilot.  He also suffers from a massive fucking ego and insecurities as HUGE AS THE SUN, making him easy to troll at first glance, but flaming an experienced /b/tard is almost impossible, due to the constant flaming that occurs in [[4chan]].  He is prone to bursts of unimaginable wisdom, but often reverts to stupidity.  Whether this is an act or just naturally how his brain works we have yet to figure out.  Has been banned from more forums than anyone on the Internets and joins even more afterwards.  

Has a Lol Degree from [[4chan|Four Leaves University]].

